{"id": "art-26", "label": "Art. 26", "title": "Art. 26", "slug": "art-26", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 26 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1367022868\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2490\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1367022868\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; exist&#259; aporturi în natur&#259;, avantaje\nacordate oric&#259;rei persoane care a participat la constituirea <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau la <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ii</span>\nconducând la acordarea <span class=SpellE>autoriza&#355;iei</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> încheiate de fondatori pe seama <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce se constituie <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npe care aceasta urmeaz&#259; s&#259; le ia asupra sa, fondatorii vor solicita\nregistratorului de registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> numirea\nunuia sau a mai multor <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;i</span>. <span\nclass=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. 38 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n39 se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_401720484\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2489\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_401720484\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Raportul expertului sau <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;ilor</span>\nva fi pus la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> subscriitorilor, la\nlocul unde urmeaz&#259; s&#259; se întruneasc&#259; adunarea constitutiv&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}